text: Ishmael Mathew Ameal Levenston (23 July 1940 â€“ 19 October 2019) was a Saban politician. He was the founder of the Saba Labour Party. Levenston died on 19 October 2019 of heart failure at a retirement center in The Bottom, aged 79. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:2019 deaths Category:Deaths from heart failure Category:Dutch politicians
